PURPOSE
-------
This project is part of academic research into cryptographic protocols,
specifically studying Schnorr signature aggregation (MuSig2) within the
MimbleWimble framework.

INTENDED USE
------------
- Educational study of cryptographic protocols
- Academic research and peer review
- Technical learning and skill development
- Open-source collaboration

